description: The image shows a conference setting with a large screen displaying a slide titled "User Journey Automation." The slide contains a circular diagram with three points labeled "Precision," "Rationale," and "Ambiguity," connected by lines to form a triangle within the circle. Below the screen, a man is working with equipment on the stage. The room is lit with a purple hue. Decorative panels are visible to the right of the screen. A patterned carpet runs throughout the room, and a partial view of a seated attendee is seen in the foreground.
